strings.Value: "Another rest without fresh meat! {name}, isn't it time you send some of your people hunting?"
"Why are you sitting there? Your meat isn't going to hunt itself!"
"Watch your tone. I shan't tolerate such ill manners."
"I would be happy to set snares, to feed my friends and companions — but I shall not take orders from anyone."
"I don't approve of Jaethal's tone, but without meat I'll be out of shape, lose my focus — and then only the gods know which of us will survive the next battle!"
"You often complain when you're sent out to hunt. And you always complain if no one else goes."
